### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:3000/post/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 2,
  "content": "This is a new post content."
}

### Get all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/post/all
Content-Type: application/json

### Get post by id
GET http://localhost:3000/post/find/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2
}

### Update post by id
PUT http://localhost:3000/post/update/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 6,
  "content": "Updated post content.",
  "updated_at": "2024-01-14 06:35:42"
}

### Delete post by id
DELETE http://localhost:3000/post/delete/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 5
}
